999827", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_1021011429333160_4176289926510597494_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7_MCG1WCAYkQ7kNvgGcpRdi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDkqGnHypqVJl8Iyg7AlDiDXMemCekpv0qkXdQafm62aA&oe=66E966E1"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "524012790104112", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001669_524012793437445_4891316513078544414_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=O79gHyPJTcYQ7kNvgGaIhWE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCoG1Zgi-iBhOtPuq6qZq8gWmbmq546_RGOAIS1mqOZXg&oe=66E97B5A"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "1187574142495669", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031470_1187574145829002_8495108821353233334_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=neBEZInW01QQ7kNvgGuT0-e&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB922eDD5rQ7O7k5ulQcCIk8ePItbXF3pUq5ZFwQZbn0g&oe=66E96DF0"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "529809686395654", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_529809689728987_2021663405477506286_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=eWk4mjInIGkQ7kNvgEgfWFN&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAifmxKA8NtKZPMgbw2fZci5mIREc_xM-72tSXxOSrN8Q&oe=66E95FFF"}, "display_name": "Cellular Safari", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellular** is an innovative virtual reality app that turns learning about **cellular biology** into an exciting adventure. Designed for **students, educators and science enthusiasts**, this app allows you to explore an **animal cell in 3D** like never before. Through an immersive interface, you can navigate through different cell structures, such as **the nucleus, mitochondria, and endoplasmic reticulum**, discovering their functions and importance.\n\nEach component of the cell is represented in stunning detail, allowing you to observe and understand complex biological processes in a visually engaging way. **Integrated artificial intelligence** is at your disposal to answer any questions you may have while exploring, providing clear and detailed explanations.\n\nCellular Safari is not just a passive educational experience; it includes a series of **mini interactive games** designed to consolidate your knowledge in a fun and engaging way. Through **challenges and quizzes**, you can test your understanding of biological concepts, making learning an active and stimulating process.\n\nPerfect for use in education or as a self-study tool, Cellular Safari offers a new and innovative way to explore the microscopic world of the animal cell. With **high-quality graphics** and an **intuitive user experience**, this app turns the study of biology into an unforgettable adventure.", "short_description": "Discover the fascinating world of the animal cell with Cell Safari, the educational VR app that allows you to explore cell structures in 3D. Through interactive mini-games and advanced artificial intelligence, learn scientific concepts while having fun. Ideal for students and biology enthusiasts, this immersive experience makes learning an exciting adventure."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "2930927027073306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974477_2930927030406639_1033799740283778117_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iGhXL_mCv2UQ7kNvgHXsAUn&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAPab1gsxVyy6Q3b6NkJ69i4ID9woTJ7RZvfLPpRMRoKA&oe=66E9598E"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "1897915367381648", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75207242_1897915370714981_6546028005331927603_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AL44k_tS2A0Q7kNvgFrxtkP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDNU0Yzp9b85Vi_y381iUPOHabpFG_qiEsioDTobfWwhw&oe=66E950CD"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1156101178831306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982713_1156101182164639_3284781712281521597_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lXkVxALZoysQ7kNvgG0RjCM&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBicWkqpiG-PBOunpI-EWq1oyNMem8JFAe7kTWIMzjI_A&oe=66E956CF"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1035480321561334", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982526_1035480328228000_568917300582159945_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=RDp9r6qvNUsQ7kNvgEaCbcB&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDZZSCGCuhaV3-A_Wpx1A7-tjiNrG67BOIrE0y_ZkjbvQ&oe=66E97938"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "840716281119571", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57574720_840716291119570_6338633741422904364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ej3NQbZwh_IQ7kNvgHpMFDT&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCVMW0iHYE2lgfBXoYiqp7m9RJccALKI9neqQ9IeuBB_g&oe=66E953DB"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "488412717275961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_488412720609294_7458364120634917665_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=I1fMvXUsjpsQ7kNvgGH0hDM&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDK6WUej_VExDscEyvSfh3DNLeoaZ0NtHpF4alLEQyehw&oe=66E97D51"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "427144199756021", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223486_427144203089354_4369279694658394896_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rmAdg1HOREoQ7kNvgF5NpwO&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCyJIICZwGN1d-lXvT1K5VNQMXSbBjmOdm7DPXw2-FybQ&oe=66E95C0F"}]}, "id": "520469743690183", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "422140790868918", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_422140794202251_1640211663921085746_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NKET3zhdqxsQ7kNvgH5eZ5b&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCyqC-MyFhmWumxmGrPIp6tXlUvRrHF3lbXaerjkTI5Bw&oe=66E9642A"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "468838062692515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984464_468838066025848_9209980070403449565_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=K8s6puP_OgoQ7kNvgEFbgMy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA4T9YcwN9npMfZsp62sr_AaEh4JJDMQjS2O77Psv_taQ&oe=66E9600C"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "481654227990009", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031353_481654234656675_3114596455803752280_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GhBuYV3bvTQQ7kNvgH36MAV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkO5vnCDEL7zNs-sAvf12uZP48JETotCiLF59RXL6jmA&oe=66E95E90"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "3889565187981667", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_3889565191315000_5528783709779854295_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ByRO4TwIWHUQ7kNvgHNoUvP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAinv0Apeumb25tnpd-oAYGJ4xy1GoHa_rU-r_suUlGYg&oe=66E95E24"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "867384681933118", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003244_867384685266451_2340853765823917163_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=z7oSEwykScsQ7kNvgEK62bH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB1g8W3A0W0BN99TDQkB5TY5JXA8O67HidD9P-syBnw2A&oe=66E96245"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "999991165259980", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476756_999991168593313_5483195490028886346_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mk4gaXlQbGgQ7kNvgFqi3_O&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDnjsl91mL553vVAZsmB3MZNa1DOwItlXpQeBx1a103hw&oe=66E96FB1"}, "display_name": "Safari Cellulare", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellulare** \u00e8 un'applicazione di realt\u00e0 virtuale innovativa che trasforma l'apprendimento della **biologia cellulare** in un'avventura emozionante. Progettata per **studenti, educatori e appassionati di scienza**, questa app ti permette di esplorare una **cellula animale in 3D** come mai prima d'ora. Attraverso un'interfaccia immersiva, puoi navigare tra le diverse strutture cellulari, come **il nucleo, i mitocondri e il reticolo endoplasmatico**, scoprendone le funzioni e l'importanza.\n\nOgni componente della cellula \u00e8 rappresentato con dettagli straordinari, permettendoti di osservare e comprendere i processi biologici complessi in modo visivamente accattivante. **L'intelligenza artificiale integrata** \u00e8 a tua disposizione per rispondere a qualsiasi domanda tu possa avere durante l'esplorazione, fornendo spiegazioni chiare e dettagliate.\n\nSafari Cellulare non \u00e8 solo un'esperienza educativa passiva; include una serie di **mini giochi interattivi** progettati per consolidare le tue conoscenze in modo divertente e coinvolgente. Attraverso **sfide e quiz**, puoi mettere alla prova la tua comprensione dei concetti biologici, rendendo l'apprendimento un processo attivo e stimolante.\n\nPerfetta per l'uso in ambito educativo o come strumento di autoapprendimento, Safari Cellulare offre un modo nuovo e innovativo per esplorare il mondo microscopico della cellula animale. Con **grafica di alta qualit\u00e0** e un'**esperienza utente intuitiva**, questa app trasforma lo studio della biologia in un'avventura indimenticabile.", "short_description": "Scopri l'affascinante mondo della cellula animale con Safari Cellulare, l'app VR educativa che ti permette di esplorare le strutture cellulari in 3D. Attraverso mini giochi interattivi e un'intelligenza artificiale avanzata, apprendi concetti scientifici divertendoti. Ideale per studenti e appassionati di biologia, questa esperienza immersiva rende l'apprendimento un'avventura entusiasmante."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_na